stigation intoa video from four yearsago showing her making what she described as \\\"an error of judgement\\\" during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9659567562698155, \"rank\": 0.03420966521913125, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation intoa video\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"four yearsago\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video showed Dujardin repeatedly hitting a student's horse with a whip from the ground.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The video\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"a student's horse\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"a whip\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her behaviour sparked widespread condemnation.\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her behaviour\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread condemnation\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complaint was made to the FEI byDutch equine lawyer Stephan Wensingon behalf of an unnamed client.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 779, \"end\": 7